name: Andrew Myers
body:
![http://www.flickr.com/photos/andrewrm/3083659041/sizes/l/in/photostream/](http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3016/3083659041_68e0435ee3_b.jpg) [View on Flickr](http://www.flickr.com/photos/andrewrm/3083659041/sizes/l/in/photostream/)

My name is Andrew. I currently live in Melbourne, Australia. You can see my [CV on Linked In](http://au.linkedin.com/pub/andrew-myers/24/727/305) 

I do DevOps. I'm currently working to help build a [broadband network](http://www.nbnco.com.au). I love vim and real shells. I play bass for [The Summervilles](http://thesummervilles.bandcamp.com/). I love bikes, but don't ride them enough.
